author: Megan Rose Dickey
title: Cowboy Ventures' Aileen Lee says enough with favoring the 'good guys'
description: Diversity and inclusion is a trash fire in Silicon Valley and in the business world at large. But let’s just focus on tech for now. At the Code Conference this evening, All Raise and Cowboy Ventures Partner Aileen Lee, shift7 CEO Megan Smith and Stubhub President Sukhinder Singh Cassidy talke…
